                  (ILESSP X ito))'                           (T (IGREATERP X ito]'          (RETURN $$VAL)))'      (PRINT "HI")'  $$ITERATE'      (SETQ X (IPLUS X (SETQ $$TEM1 iby)))'      (GO $$LP))'(for X from ifrom to ito by iby do (PRINT "HI"))'82_DRIBBLE]'Workaround: Test Case: Edit-By: MasinterEdit-Date:  1-Sep-84 15':56':42